curl http://my-service.backend.svc.cluster.local:<port>

(try curl http://my-service.backend:8080 - might work)




            *** Update repos to the latest versions

1 get image name from existing release from "helm list"
2 find actual name <CHART_NAME>/<IMAGE> using "helm search repo"
3 upgrade using:
    helm upgrade RELEASE_NAME CHART_NAME/IMAGE --version=<VERSION_NUMBER>

