            ***

            NetworkPolicy

To allow traffic on port 80:

      ingress:
      - from:
        - ports:
          - protocol: TCP
            port: 80


            ***

HTTPRoute to redirect traffic use weight

    backendRefs:
    - name: web-service
      port: 80
      weight: 80
    - name: web-service-v2
      port: 80
      weight: 20

        ***

        Node affinity to run on a specific node :

   nodeAffinity:
     required:
       nodeSelectorTerms:
         - matchExpressions:
             - key: kubernetes.io/hostname
               operator: In
               values:
                 - cluster1-controlplane


